reviewText: Excellent Training video best on basic survival plants I've found. This video is great for beginner's to learn plants that help you survive you got to watch several times to remember the content be sure to do that!!!
I wish it covered more plants!  bob45ana youtube channel had a lot of plants.  The DvD is good, but it could be better!
This is excellent, very informative, but could use more plants from the east coast.  Loaded with info, very helpful, would highly recommend.
